nodes.text: A general of the Galactic Empire was present at Kessendra Stadium on Kessel when the Central Committee of Grand Moffs proclaimed the mutant slavelord Trioculus to be the son of Emperor Palpatine, and therefore the next ruler of the Empire. Following a demonstration of Trioculus' so-called Force powers, the general expressed eagerness to be the first attendant of the ceremony to pledge his loyalty to him, but was pipped to the post by one of the Grand Moffs.
